<h2>ESL Bingo Formats</h2>
<h3>Vocabulary Bingo</h3>
<p>Cards contain target vocabulary words. The teacher calls definitions, synonyms, or uses the word in a sentence. Students identify and mark the matching word. This format works for any vocabulary unit — animals, food, jobs, emotions, etc.</p>
<h3>Spelling Bingo</h3>
