                'meta_description' => 'Running a bingo tournament? Learn the official structure, scoring systems, tie-breaking rules, and how to manage a multi-session bingo competition.',
                'excerpt'          => 'A bingo tournament adds serious competitive stakes to the game. Here\'s how to structure rounds, track points, break ties, and crown a champion.',
                'body'             => '<p>A single-night bingo game is fun, but a multi-round tournament takes the excitement to a completely different level. Tournaments create ongoing competition, build anticipation between sessions, and produce a clear champion — perfect for clubs, fundraisers, and recurring community events.</p>
